headline: Nasdaq price target raised to $116 from $113 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley analyst Michael Cyprys raised the firm’s price target on Nasdaq (NDAQ) to $116 from $113 and keeps an Overweight rating on the shares.
